" Vanilla mappings
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" On insert mode, Shift-Tab to unindent
inoremap <S-Tab> <C-D>
" On visual mode, use tab and shift tab to indent the current selected text
vnoremap <Tab> >gv
vnoremap <S-Tab> <gv

